383
00:21:09,358 --> 00:21:11,650
--Listen up!
--I'm listening.

384
00:21:11,733 --> 00:21:12,525
It's time!

385
00:21:12,608 --> 00:21:13,775
For what?

386
00:21:13,858 --> 00:21:17,650
