our very first CD!

387
00:21:17,733 --> 00:21:19,192
--Whoa!
--Huh?

388
00:21:19,275 --> 00:21:20,900
Are you serious?

389
00:21:20,983 --> 00:21:23,442
'Course I'm serious, why would
I lie about somethin' like that?

390
00:21:23,525 --> 00:21:28,025
Aww yeah! Now a buncha people
all across the whole wide world

391
00:21:28,108 --> 00:21:29,942
will get to hear Saku singing!

392
00:21:30,025 --> 00:21:32,942
That's right! We'll get
to show off our vocalist!

393
00:21:33,025 --> 00:21:35,817
