I'm so happy I met you two.

404
00:22:03,692 --> 00:22:05,358
I never knew I
could enjoy anything

405
00:22:05,442 --> 00:22:07,775
as much as our time together.

406
00:22:07,858 --> 00:22:10,108
Uta, Sosuke.

407
00:22:10,192 --> 00:22:13,317
